members.description: Connectivity is restored for adapter in slot 3, port 5.

eventDetails.eventItemValue: This trap will be sent any time connectivity is restored to a logical adapter. This occurs when the physical adapter in a single adapter configuration returns to the OK condition or at least one physical adapter in a logical adapter group returns to the OK condition. This can be caused by replacement of a faulty cable or re-attaching a cable that was unplugged. User Action: None required.
